item.title: What Is Adelaide Cottage? - Inside Prince Harry and Meghan Markle's New Home from Queen Elizabeth
item.description: Queen Elizabeth II and Prince Harry's special bond is no secret. It's even been rumored that the Duke of Sussex is Her Majesty's favorite grandchild, and her latest wedding present might just prove that rumor true. According to The Daily Mail, the Queen has gifted Harry and his wife, Meghan Markle, a beautiful home. The estate, named Adelaide Cottage, has been a longtime residence of royal family members, and it is the second house that the Queen has given her youngest grandson.
